data.description: Enjoy the peace and quiet in this quaint and cozy cabin. Snuggle up by the fire or open the windows and let in all the natural light. There is plenty of deck space to enjoy the cool mountain air while you sip your coffee and watch the wildlife. There are 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with an open living space. It is the perfect mountain getaway!
